org.jasig.cas.services

Class DefaultServicesManagerImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jasig.cas.services.DefaultServicesManagerImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ReloadableServicesManager, ServicesManager, org.springframework.beans.factory.Aware, org.springframework.context.ApplicationEventPublisherAware

    @Component(value="servicesManager")
public class DefaultServicesManagerImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements ReloadableServicesManager, org.springframework.context.ApplicationEventPublisherAware
    Default implementation of the ServicesManager interface. If there are no services registered with the server, it considers the ServicecsManager disabled and will not prevent any service from using CAS.
    Since:
    3.1
